            "title": "Health benefits &amp; Uses of Mad Honey",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>The health benefits of Mad Honey is a primary trigger for wellness communities and holistic health seekers while the recreational use is secondary one. This wild honey sourced from Rhododendron Flowers and some other wildflowers have been used as a traditional medicine for a long time. The <a href=\"https://medicinalmadhoney.com/\" title=\"Original Mad Honey from Nepal\">Mad Honey</a> has been well known in the Gurung ethnic community of Nepal as well as in some regions of Turkey as a tonic for restoring several health alignments. With 100% organic and high nutritional value the mad honey has been known as a life extending elixir from the cliffs. This has further sparked the growing interest and the demand along with the use for this product is inclining.<br/><br/></p>",
