      "name": "Table Basmil",
      "settings": {
        "main_heading": "Use of Mad Honey in Folk Medicine",
        "main_content": "<p>The use of Mad Honey as a folk medicine has been in practice since the onset of <a href=\"/pages/honey-hunting-tour\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tour\">honey hunting</a>. The <a href=\"/pages/honey-hunter\" title=\"Honey Hunters\">Gurung Honey hunters of Nepal </a>who have harnessed the medicinal effects of Mad Honey have been putting their lives at risk to harvest this rare medicinal elixir. They have been using Mad Honey traditionally for treating several health alignments.</p>",
        "alignment": "center",
        "valignment": "center",
        "content_part_width": "120rem",
        "section_padding": "12rem 16px",
        "section_margin": "0 auto",
