      "name": "FAQ",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Mad Honey uses at home",
        "description": "Mad Honey can be used to enhance holistic health considering the potential benefits.The use of Mad Honey depends on the intent of effect one is expecting. Some use Mad Honey to enhance their holistic health and overall wellness while some use it purely for the purpose of recreation.\n<br><br>\nBut whatever the intent is, The best way to consume Mad Honey is to open the lid, dig one spoon and shove directly on the tongue. \n<br><br>\nAlthough the use of Mad Honey with potential health benefits is evident enough, a slight overdose can bring in negative side effects. Thus, it is always advised to follow mad honey dose guidelines before trying the mad honey.",
