          "settings": {
            "title": "Safe use of Mad Honey",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>While the benefits of Mad Honey seem a positive green flag the overdose <a href=\"/pages/mad-honey-effects\" title=\"Mad Honey Effects\">effects of Mad Honey</a> can be fatal. Thus, it is necessary to practice safe usage of Mad Honey and keep things in mind before taking<br/></p><ul><li>Follow dosage guideline of Mad Honey including start low and maintain per day consumption limits</li><li>Find if <a href=\"/pages/is-mad-honey-legal\" title=\"Is Mad Honey Legal?\">Mad Honey is legal</a> or not to avoid legal circumstances</li><li>Avoid if you have existing heart problems</li><li>Seek medical consultation if you have existing health conditions or allergies with honey and pollen</li><li>Pregnant women and children should avoid at any cost</li><li>Always find authentic and verified Mad Honey to avoid synthetic effects of chemicals</li><li>Avoid mixing mad honey with other psychoactive substances, stimulants and depressants</li></ul>",
            "button_text": "",
